{{Administrative divisions of Brunei sidebar}}{{Politics of Brunei}} A '''[[mukim]]''' is the second-level [[Administrative divisions of Brunei|administrative division]] of [[Brunei]], and the primary subdivision of a [[Districts of Brunei|district]]. The community is headed by a {{Lang|ms|[[penghulu]]}}. A mukim is further divided into [[Villages of Brunei|villages]] ({{Lang-ms|kampung}} or {{Lang|ms|kampong}}).<ref name=":0" />
